<p>The table below shows the different <a href="/wiki/Affix" title="Affix">affixes</a> attached to the preterite aspect of the verb root PRS "to decide"; and as can be seen, the <a href="/wiki/Grammatical_gender" title="Grammatical gender">grammatical genders</a> differ only in the second person singular and third person plural.
</p>
<table class="wikitable">

<tbody><tr>
<th>
</th>
<th>G-Stem
