</td></tr>
</tbody></table>
<h5><span id="Suffixed_.28or_enclitic.29_pronouns"></span><span class="mw-headline" id="Suffixed_(or_enclitic)_pronouns">Suffixed (or enclitic) pronouns</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Akkadian_language&amp;action=edit&amp;section=27" title="Edit section: Suffixed (or enclitic) pronouns">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h5>
