<h4><span class="mw-headline" id="Demonstrative_pronouns">Demonstrative pronouns</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Akkadian_language&amp;action=edit&amp;section=28" title="Edit section: Demonstrative pronouns">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h4>
<p><a href="/wiki/Demonstrative_pronoun" class="mw-redirect" title="Demonstrative pronoun">Demonstrative pronouns</a> in Akkadian differ from the <a href="/wiki/West_Semitic_languages" title="West Semitic languages">Western Semitic</a> variety. The following table shows the Akkadian demonstrative pronouns according to near and far <a href="/wiki/Deixis" title="Deixis">deixis</a>:
