</div>
<div class="interlinear"><div style="float: left; margin-bottom: 0.3em;margin-right: 1em;"><p lang="akk" style="margin: 0px;font-style: italic;">l≈´</p><p style="margin: 0px;">or</p></div><div style="float: left; margin-bottom: 0.3em;margin-right: 1em;"><p lang="akk" style="margin: 0px;font-style: italic;">alp-am</p><p style="margin: 0px;">cattle/oxen-<abbr class="gloss-abbr" title="accusative case" style="font-variant: small-caps; font-variant-numeric: oldstyle-nums; text-transform: lowercase;"><a href="/wiki/Accusative_case" title="Accusative case">ACC</a></abbr></p></div><div style="float: left; margin-bottom: 0.3em;margin-right: 1em;"><p lang="akk" style="margin: 0px;font-style: italic;">l≈´</p><p style="margin: 0px;">or</p></div><div style="float: left; margin-bottom: 0.3em;margin-right: 1em;"><p lang="akk" style="margin: 0px;font-style: italic;">immer-am</p><p style="margin: 0px;">sheep-<abbr class="gloss-abbr" title="accusative case" style="font-variant: small-caps; font-variant-numeric: oldstyle-nums; text-transform: lowercase;"><a href="/wiki/Accusative_case" title="Accusative case">ACC</a></abbr></p></div><div style="float: left; margin-bottom: 0.3em;margin-right: 1em;"><p lang="akk" style="margin: 0px;font-style: italic;">l≈´</p><p style="margin: 0px;">or</p></div><div style="float: left; margin-bottom: 0.3em;margin-right: 1em;"><p lang="akk" style="margin: 0px;font-style: italic;">imƒìr-am</p><p style="margin: 0px;">donkey-<abbr class="gloss-abbr" title="accusative case" style="font-variant: small-caps; font-variant-numeric: oldstyle-nums; text-transform: lowercase;"><a href="/wiki/Accusative_case" title="Accusative case">ACC</a></abbr></p></div><div style="float: left; margin-bottom: 0.3em;margin-right: 1em;"><p lang="akk" style="margin: 0px;font-style: italic;">≈´</p><p style="margin: 0px;">and</p></div><div style="float: left; margin-bottom: 0.3em;margin-right: 1em;"><p lang="akk" style="margin: 0px;font-style: italic;">l≈´</p><p style="margin: 0px;">or</p></div><div style="float: left; margin-bottom: 0.3em;margin-right: 1em;"><p lang="akk" style="margin: 0px;font-style: italic;">mimma ≈°um≈°u</p><p style="margin: 0px;">something</p></div><div style="float: left; margin-bottom: 0.3em;margin-right: 1em;"><p lang="akk" style="margin: 0px;font-style: italic;">ina</p><p style="margin: 0px;">from</p></div><p style="display: none;">l≈´ alp-am l≈´ immer-am l≈´ imƒìr-am ≈´ l≈´ {mimma ≈°um≈°u} ina</p><p style="display: none;">or cattle/oxen-ACC or sheep-ACC or donkey-ACC and or something from</p><p class="mw-empty-elt"></p><div style="clear: left; display: block;"></div>
</div>
<div class="interlinear"><div style="float: left; margin-bottom: 0.3em;margin-right: 1em;"><p lang="akk" style="margin: 0px;font-style: italic;">qƒÅt</p><p style="margin: 0px;">hand-<abbr class="gloss-abbr" title="Status Constructus" style="font-variant: small-caps; font-variant-numeric: oldstyle-nums; text-transform: lowercase;"><a href="/wiki/Construct_state" title="Construct state">CONST</a></abbr></p></div><div style="float: left; margin-bottom: 0.3em;margin-right: 1em;"><p lang="akk" style="margin: 0px;font-style: italic;">mƒÅr</p><p style="margin: 0px;">son-<abbr class="gloss-abbr" title="Status Constructus" style="font-variant: small-caps; font-variant-numeric: oldstyle-nums; text-transform: lowercase;"><a href="/wiki/Construct_state" title="Construct state">CONST</a></abbr></p></div><div style="float: left; margin-bottom: 0.3em;margin-right: 1em;"><p lang="akk" style="margin: 0px;font-style: italic;">awƒ´l-im</p><p style="margin: 0px;">man-<abbr class="gloss-abbr" title="genitive case" style="font-variant: small-caps; font-variant-numeric: oldstyle-nums; text-transform: lowercase;"><a href="/wiki/Genitive_case" title="Genitive case">GEN</a></abbr></p></div><div style="float: left; margin-bottom: 0.3em;margin-right: 1em;"><p lang="akk" style="margin: 0px;font-style: italic;">≈´</p><p style="margin: 0px;">and</p></div><div style="float: left; margin-bottom: 0.3em;margin-right: 1em;"><p lang="akk" style="margin: 0px;font-style: italic;">l≈´</p><p style="margin: 0px;">or</p></div><div style="float: left; margin-bottom: 0.3em;margin-right: 1em;"><p lang="akk" style="margin: 0px;font-style: italic;">warad</p><p style="margin: 0px;">slave-<abbr class="gloss-abbr" title="Status Constructus" style="font-variant: small-caps; font-variant-numeric: oldstyle-nums; text-transform: lowercase;"><a href="/wiki/Construct_state" title="Construct state">CONST</a></abbr></p></div><div style="float: left; margin-bottom: 0.3em;margin-right: 1em;"><p lang="akk" style="margin: 0px;f