</div>
<div class="interlinear"><div style="float: left; margin-bottom: 0.3em;margin-right: 1em;"><p lang="akk" style="margin: 0px;font-style: italic;">riks-ƒÅtim</p><p style="margin: 0px;">contracts-<abbr class="gloss-abbr" title="genitive case" style="font-variant: small-caps; font-variant-numeric: oldstyle-nums; text-transform: lowercase;"><a href="/wiki/Genitive_case" title="Genitive case">GEN</a></abbr></p></div><div style="float: left; margin-bottom: 0.3em;margin-right: 1em;"><p lang="akk" style="margin: 0px;font-style: italic;">i-≈°tƒÅm-√ò</p><p style="margin: 0px;">bought-<abbr class="gloss-abbr" title="third person" style="font-variant: small-caps; font-variant-numeric: oldstyle-nums; text-transform: lowercase;"><a href="/wiki/Grammatical_person" title="Grammatical person">3</a></abbr>.<abbr class="gloss-abbr" title="singular number" style="font-variant: small-caps; font-variant-numeric: oldstyle-nums; text-transform: lowercase;"><a href="/wiki/Singular_number" class="mw-redirect" title="Singular number">SG</a></abbr>.<abbr class="gloss-abbr" title="perfect" style="font-variant: small-caps; font-variant-numeric: oldstyle-nums; text-transform: lowercase;"><a href="/wiki/Perfect_(grammar)" title="Perfect (grammar)">PERF</a></abbr></p></div><div style="float: left; margin-bottom: 0.3em;margin-right: 1em;"><p lang="akk" style="margin: 0px;font-style: italic;">≈´</p><p style="margin: 0px;">and</p></div><div style="float: left; margin-bottom: 0.3em;margin-right: 1em;"><p lang="akk" style="margin: 0px;font-style: italic;">l≈´</p><p style="margin: 0px;">or</p></div><div style="float: left; margin-bottom: 0.3em;margin-right: 1em;"><p lang="akk" style="margin: 0px;font-style: italic;">ana</p><p style="margin: 0px;">for</p></div><div style="float: left; margin-bottom: 0.3em;margin-right: 1em;"><p lang="akk" style="margin: 0px;font-style: italic;">ma·π£·π£ƒÅr≈´t-im</p><p style="margin: 0px;">safekeeping-<abbr class="gloss-abbr" title="genitive case" style="font-variant: small-caps; font-variant-numeric: oldstyle-nums; text-transform: lowercase;"><a href="/wiki/Genitive_case" title="Genitive case">GEN</a></abbr></p></div><div style="float: left; margin-bottom: 0.3em;margin-right: 1em;"><p lang="akk" style="margin: 0px;font-style: italic;">i-m·∏´ur-√ò</p><p style="margin: 0px;">received-<abbr class="gloss-abbr" title="third person" style="font-variant: small-caps; font-variant-numeric: oldstyle-nums; text-transform: lowercase;"><a href="/wiki/Grammatical_person" title="Grammatical person">3</a></abbr>.<abbr class="gloss-abbr" title="singular number" style="font-variant: small-caps; font-variant-numeric: oldstyle-nums; text-transform: lowercase;"><a href="/wiki/Singular_number" class="mw-redirect" title="Singular number">SG</a></abbr>.<abbr class="gloss-abbr" title="preterite" style="font-variant: small-caps; font-variant-numeric: oldstyle-nums; text-transform: lowercase;"><a href="/wiki/Preterite" title="Preterite">PRET</a></abbr></p></div><p style="display: none;">riks-ƒÅtim i-≈°tƒÅm-√ò ≈´ l≈´ ana ma·π£·π£ƒÅr≈´t-im i-m·∏´ur-√ò</p><p style="display: none;">contracts-GEN bought-3.SG.PERF and or for safekeeping-GEN received-3.SG.PRET</p><p class="mw-empty-elt"></p><div style="clear: left; display: block;"></div>
</div>
<div class="interlinear"><div style="float: left; margin-bottom: 0.3em;margin-right: 1em;"><p lang="akk" style="margin: 0px;font-style: italic;">awƒ´l-um</p><p style="margin: 0px;">man-<abbr class="gloss-abbr" title="nominative case" style="font-variant: small-caps; font-variant-numeric: oldstyle-nums; text-transform: lowercase;"><a href="/wiki/Nominative_case" title="Nominative case">NOM</a></abbr></p></div><div style="float: left; margin-bottom: 0.3em;margin-right: 1em;"><p lang="akk" style="margin: 0px;font-style: italic;">≈°≈´</p><p style="margin: 0px;">he-<abbr class="gloss-abbr" title="third person" style="font-variant: small-caps; font-variant-numeric: oldstyle-nums; text-transform: lowercase;"><a href="/wiki/Grammatical_person" title="Grammatical person">3</a></abbr>.<abbr class="gloss-abbr" title="masculine gender" style="font-variant: small-caps; font-variant-numeric: oldstyle-nums; text-transform: lowercase;"><a href="/wiki/Masculine_gender" class="mw-redirect" title="Masculine gender">M</a></abbr>.<abbr class="gloss-abbr" title="singular number" style="font-variant: small-caps; font-variant-numeric: oldstyle-nums; text-transform: lowercase;"><a href="/wiki/Singular_number" class="mw-redirect" title="Singular number">SG</a></abbr></p></div><div style="float: left; margin-bottom: 0.3em;margin-right: 1em;"><p lang="akk" style="margin: 0px;font-style: italic;">≈°arrƒÅq</p><p style="margin: 0px;">stealer-<abbr class="gloss-abbr" title="Status Absolutus" style="font-variant: small-caps; font-variant-numeric: oldstyle-nums; text-transform: lowercase;"><a href="/wiki/Absolute_state" class="mw-redirect" title="Absolute state">ABS</a></abbr></p></div><div style="float: left; margin-bottom: 0.3em;margin-right: 1em;"><p lang="akk" style="margin: 0px;font-style: italic;">i-ddƒÅk</p><p style="margin: 0px;">is_killed-<abbr class="gloss-abbr" title="third person" style="font-variant: small-caps; font-variant-numeric: oldstyle-nums; text-transform: lowercase;"><a href="/wiki/Grammatical_person" title="Grammatical person">3</a></abbr>.<abbr class="gloss-abbr" title="singular number" style="font-variant: small-caps; font-variant-numeric: oldstyle-nums; text-transform: lowercase;"><a href="/wiki/Singular_number" class="mw-redirect" title="Singular number">SG</a></abbr>.<abbr class="gloss-abbr" title="passive voice" style="font-variant: small-caps; font-variant-numeric: oldstyle-nums; text-transform: lowercase;"><a href="/wiki/Passive_voice" title="Passive voice">PASS</a></abbr>-<abbr class="gloss-abbr" title="present tense" style="font-variant: small-caps; font-variant-numeric: oldstyle-nums; text-transform: lowercase;"><a href="/wiki/Present_tense" title="Present tense">PRS</a></abbr></p></div><p style="display: none;">awƒ´l-um ≈°≈´ ≈°arrƒÅq i-ddƒÅk</p><p style="display: none;">man-NOM he-3.M.SG stealer-<abbr class="gloss-abbr" title="Status Absolutus" style="font-variant: small-caps; font-variant-numeric: oldstyle-nums; text-transform: lowercase;"><a href="/wiki/Absolute_state" class="mw-redirect" title="Absolute state">ABS</a></abbr> is_killed-3.SG.PASS-PRS</p><p class="mw-empty-elt"></p><div style="clear: left; display: block;"></div>
</div>
<p>Translation:
</p>
<dl><dd><i>If a man has bought silver or gold, a male or a female slave,<br />an ox, a sheep, or a donkey‚Äîor anything for that matter‚Äî<br />from another man or from another man‚Äôs slave without witnesses or contract,<br />or if he accepted something for safekeeping without same,<br />then this man is a thief and hence to be killed.</i></dd></dl>
<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Akkadian_literature">Akkadian literature</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Akkadian_language&amp;action=edit&amp;section=38" title="Edit section: Akkadian literature">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
